Lock Screen: while watching video you can lock screen to prevent interruption from accidentally touching your screen. Timed comments: You can now add timed comments without leaving the full screen mode. Video Settings: We aggregated video related controls under settings gear icon. You can configure timed comments subtitle and more by tapping on the settings icon in video page. Spotlight: You can now search for a Viki show in spotlight search on your iPhone or iPad. You asked for it you get it. Ratings and reviews is now here in the Viki iOS app! Rate and review your favorite shows right in the app! Not sure what to watch Why not start with our top rated shows reviewed by YOU!We also squished a few nasty bugs so that you can get the best experience possible! Also Viki has a new logo! The R in the new Viki logo reflects the fact that Viki is now a part of the Rakuten Group of companies. Tokyo based Rakuten Inc. one of the world s largest internet services companies acquired Viki in 2013 allowing Viki to join Viber eBates Lyft and other Rakuten sister companies to reach a global online audience of nearly 1 billion users. Expect more great things from Viki as we bring you more of your favorite primetime global TV shows and movies!
Hot on the heels of our 4.0.0 release for iOS 9 we have fixed our top crashes and improved the stability of the app.

Our team has worked extra hard to get Viki ready for iOS 9 to bring you split screen multitasking for the iPad Air 2 and other other devices that support this in the future ! Now you would be able to watch your favorite shows while doing other things. Along with this we have also fixed lots of bugs and other UI refinements. Enjoy!

We know how much you like your favourite Celebrities so we have searched the web far and wide to bring you even more information for your enjoyment. Also we have been listening to your feedback to fix issues and improve the overall performance of the app. Hope you continue enjoying your shows!

In this update we ve improved our sign up and login flow. We also added new ways to group shows into collections so its easier to discovery new content. And as always this update also includes lots of bug fixes and performance improvements.

We re excited to share a new way to experience timed comments. We ve added a new awesome mode where you will be able to scroll and add timed comments previously you could only add when watching from our website . We can t wait for you to try it out and let us know what you think. BONUS! We ve also updated the app to be optimized for the iPhone 6 and 6 Plus for a better viewing experience. Happy watching!

We just made a few minor UI tweaks and bug fixes! We would love for you to leave a review and share with us your thoughts about the new feature. Alternatively you can drop us an email at mobile viki.com.

Check out our new feature Celebrities! Know more about your favorite actors and actresses like their biography blood type and star sign. You can also see a list of all the works they have done and awards they have received. We also added cast members on a lot of TV Shows. We would love for you to leave a review and share with us your thoughts about the new feature. Alternatively you can drop us an email at mobile viki.com.

Introducing the On Air Calendar on Viki Keep track and stay tune to your favorite shows from each week! We would love for you to leave a review and share with us your thoughts about the new feature. Alternatively you can drop us an email at mobile viki.com.
We fixed an issue where our player might become unresponsive under certain conditions. If you are enjoying Viki please let us know what you think by leaving us a a review. Thanks so much!

IMPORTANT ANNOUNCEMENT For updating users: we found an issue in 3.9.0 that makes the video player unresponsive under certain conditions please hold off updating until 3.9.1. For those that have already updated please hang in there a fix is on the way. We did a lot of bug fixes and improvement on performance. You ll also see a new link to our Viki Blog . Get updates about the latest celebrity news and updates from us!
